    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《魔王斗勇者：和平缔造者・序章》是一款短篇「王道」RPG，你将扮演魔王的妹妹，讨伐勇者王，迈出征服人类的第一步。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不太王道的王道RPG</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一样是勇者对魔王的套路，你这次却不是扮演勇者；不只能从新的视角看奇幻世界，还能体验魔王是如何诞生！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>满足各种需求的难度选项</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只想好好读一则故事，还是渴望挑战强大的敌人？本作难度包含「无战斗模式」到「极限模式」，满足不同玩家的需求！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不必农的回合制战斗</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摆脱刷等级、农道具！只要善用伙伴的长处，痛击敌人的弱点，便能克敌制胜！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重启《魔王：和平缔造者》</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作是《和平缔造者系列》的序章，而《和平缔造者系列》则是《魔王：和平缔造者》的重启，在维持原作气氛的前提之下，扩大了故事的格局。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796080/extras/8ebbe157fd3098dd648aa0dc61e343cc.avif?t=1735294977\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796080/extras/0ff237909fd0941958c5a39715e3b4ae.avif?t=1735294977\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796080/extras/1d1dd516aea80cc2f5a6527f21cd32a0.avif?t=1735294977\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796080/extras/7571510b53a65e59ecfabf158812d28a.avif?t=1735294977\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >直播与游戏实况之规范</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许直播与游戏实况。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >允许营利，但仅限于以影音网站的功能营利。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若能在直播或游戏实况的标题加入游戏名称，或在说明栏列出Steam页面的连结，我方将不胜感激。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直播与游戏实况所导致的任何损害，我方概不负责。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本规范如有变更，恕不另行通知。</p></li></ul>",
